dc_title_s: Fire Department Response Districts Rock County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Fire Department response districts in Rock County, Wisconsin in 2020.[The Fire shapefile depicts the fire and EMS response boundaries within Rock County including a few areas where Rock County agencies respond to bordering counties. It also shows a few areas where out-of-county fire/EMS agencies respond within Rock County. This dataset is for Rock County 911 Communications Center purposes only.
